---
title: Warm Panzanella Salad (V) with Chilli and Crumbled Feta
description: This isn't your normal salad. Bursting with fresh veg which have been combined with the sharp flavour of capers and a kick of heat from the Chilli Flakes. Paired with fresh Butternut Squash and creamy Feta cheese, this is one of our favourite recipes and we’re pretty sure it’s about to become yours too.
